{"tid":1564284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇ching啲朋友講野都好撚直接？","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T17:08:06.000Z","uid":212569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0670ebda9d95f98cabd08dac8e767a1b5c5d0805","tid":1564284,"uid":212569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"自己本身之前返工識落一個男同事，我啱啱入職嗰陣佢係第一個R我傾計嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，本身都覺得佢幾nice，跟著之後返返下發覺呢個同事講野真係好撚掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成撚日窒住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n因為之前係返零售業，有次我要拎新貨比客人，跟著我睇唔到件貨喺貨倉上面，我咁啱睇唔到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢就好撚惡咁串尻我發雞盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，串完我之後又繼續R我吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好似自以為自己好風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實應該點樣應付呢啲人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋係咪好多男仔講野都咁撚直？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs: 估到我嘅盡量勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef8bec17d03b772073459e83cb0300f49cf11b9","tid":1564284,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:49:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span